##Repositories
[awsshellscript](https://github.com/TMitch15/awsshellscript)
* In this repository is a script that allows me to auto update my web server and install the latest Apache update.

[awsshellscript2](https://github.com/TMitch15/awsshellscript2)
* In this repository the scripts for creating a development server are available and will allow you to install a basic version with no trouble.

[s2employeedb](https://github.com/TMitch15/s2employeedb)
* In this repository there is a basic database program using SQL to simulate have employees in a list.
